\begin_layout Standard
In addition to the standard processing that produces the variables in this
 subsection, an alternate processor is available that provides some additional
 options and capabilities, including the production of two sets of variables
 that include either all particles or all particles that pass a roundness
 test.
 Additional options include different ways of defining the particle size
 (including circle fitting or sizing based on the dimension along the direction
 of flight.
 Corrections to sizing are made to account for diffraction, and a shattering
 correction can be applied based on interarrival times.
 Some categories of spurious images (e.g., 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

streakers
